{
  "stem": "3475.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you-- getting back into the life of Auschwitz, you know, that-- the daily hardship of getting enough food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I remember, we used to get coffee there which wasn't fit to drink.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to-- I used to brush my teeth with that coffee, you know, because it was something warm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to get a slice of-- slice of salami and a slice of bread and a bowl of soup, you know, which if the-- if the man that was dishing up the soup liked you, he would scoop it down from the bottom.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you'd have something, you know, to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If he didn't-- if he didn't know you, he would give you from the top.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It would be mostly water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a daily struggle to-- getting enough food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to sneak behind the kitchen to get some potato peels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we could eat the potato peels just for sustenance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and then, periodic-- another thing that happened to me in Auschwitz that-- I, I had a toothache a couple times.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had some bad teeth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, they didn't bother fixing them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just yanked them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, that's how I lost some of my teeth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because once you start losing teeth, it affects the other teeth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my teeth got progressively worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Another time, I remember that I was eating some bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it must have been spoiled bread because I got deathly sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my temperature shot up-- way up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was feverish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took me to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they pumped-- they shoved the tube down my throat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put some suction on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they emptied my stomach.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
